  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110250/extras/34844e6f879744bac3d1dabc448b67dd.avif?t=1737797773\" width=610 height=1526 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >♣ What kind of game is ️ Calice?</h2><br>Calice is a card strategy deck building game.<br>It's a game in which Alice who falls into a strange country escapes from a strange country with the help of various people.<br>It is a game that uses various cards to defeat enemies and experience various events in the process of escaping.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110250/extras/38c01392721c075f6c6c3e5b3f080422.avif?t=1737797773\" width=610 height=342 /></span><br><br><strong>Choose the path you want to take through various options!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110250/extras/8fa97e1c63877b3f237e76a42e339576.avif?t=1737797773\" width=610 height=342 /></span><br><br><strong>Let's attack the enemy by putting the right number in the combine card!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110250/extras/26d36d09530854de735c0c03ace44f7d.avif?t=1737797773\" width=610 height=342 /></span><br><br><strong>Various items that can be purchased through caterpillars!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110250/extras/578ea4540fdc48ca7005a608fb38363a.avif?t=1737797773\" width=610 height=342 /></span><br><br><strong>A break with friends who help the player!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110250/extras/dbde68f7bb2bfaa624589e5b3e768a1e.avif?t=1737797773\" width=610 height=343 /></span><br><br><strong>A chance to get multiple items and cards through various events!</strong>",
